{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your very own workmate cat, Purrounding</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unorganized wallpapers, file clutter...<br>Whether you're working, studying, or just staring at a blank screen, spend some time with your personalized cat through Purrounding!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/extras/purrwalking.gif?t=1736350631\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Left alone, the cat will walk on your taskbar, curl up like a loaf of bread, and just hang out on your screen. You can use your mouse to interact with your cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can customize your cat to your liking. Change their fur color, eye color, and even add different patterns to make your cat unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why not have a clock with a Pomodoro timer when you need to focus?<br>You can also listen to soothing lo-fi music on the radio to help you focus on your work. Customize and arrange your screen with a variety of other furniture pieces.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736350631","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736350631","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/42bb75dbe418a5a921cc05ec3ea9e5f710136534/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736350631","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244420/42bb75dbe418a5a921cc05ec3ea9e5f710136534/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736350631","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your very own wo